==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Smeller
<hw>Smell"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
smells, or perceives by the sense of smell; one who gives out
smell.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The nose.</def> <mark>[Pugilists' Slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Smell-feast</ent>⟦br⟧
